profile:
Welcome to Devlin Property Maintenance,

Our team takes great pride in offering high-quality landscape services to the Ottawa area for over 10 years.  From softscaping to hardscaping we can provide and maintain a beautiful landscape.

Leave you lawn, garden & landscape to us. we've got you covered!
-Devlin Property Maintenance, 613-229-9307, www.DevlinPM.ca

-Lawn Mowing/Maintenance
-Lawn Dethatching

-Lawn Pest Control (Licensed)
-Lawn Sod & Seed Installation
-Lawn Excavation
